<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 5 (Xinhua) -- Former world number one Jim
Courier of the United States fulfilled his dream to win the title
of China Open on Sunday, beating Sweden's Magnus Gustafsson 7-6
(12-10), 3-6, 6-3.
</P>
