<HEADLINE> Exhibition Attracts 1.2 Million Visitors </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 5 (Xinhua) -- The largest ever exhibition of
China's wide-ranging achievements in all areas over the past
five years closed here today.
</P>
<P>
The one-month exhibition attracted over 1.2 million visitors
from throughout the nation, including high-ranking Party and
government leaders such as Jiang Zemin, Li Peng, and over 2000
delegates to the 15th National Congress of the Communist Party of
China (CPC) which was convened on September 12-18 of this year,
