</P>
<P>
Mongkon presented Li with a letter from Thai Prime Minister
Chavalit Yongchaiyudh, and said both Chavalit and the Thai
government sincerely appreciated Chinese government's support and
assistance during Thailand's Financial and economic crisis.
</P>
<P>
Li asked Mongkon to convey his best regards to Chavalit upon
his return home.
</P>
<P>
Fu Quanyou, member of the Central Military Commission and chief
of the General Staff of the Chinese People's Liberation Army
(PLA), was among those present at the meeting.  
</P>
</TEXT>
