the Indonesian Soccer Association are not the FBI (the US Federal
Bureau of Investigation) nor the police."
</P>
<P>
"Although we've been fighting bribery for the last 10 years it
still exists," he said, adding that any bribery would have to
involve a player.
</P>
<P>
"The player should never take the offer," he was quoted as
saying.
</P>
<P>
The eight nation football tournament starts with four matches
on Sunday. The final will be held at the Senayan stadium here on
October 18. 
