<P>
SOFIA, October 4 (Xinhua) - The 43rd General Assembly of the
Atlantic Treaty Association (ATA), which opened here Saturday, has
discussed the eastward expansion of the North Atlantic Treaty
Organization (NATO).
</P>
<P>
Summarizing the discussions on the reform of NATO and the
United Nations, Italian representative Emilio Colombo said
European states and the United States must coordinate their
positions on NATO enlargement.
</P>
