<P>
Worns rested a sore upper leg muscle on Wednesday when Bayer
Leverkusen were savaged 4-0 by Monaco in the European Champions
League. He came back for Saturday's 2-1 Bundesliga win over
Duisburg but aggravated the injury and had to leave the field
just before half-time. 
</P>
</TEXT>
